      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/01/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/01/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Node-js"><a href="#Node-js" class="headerlink" title="Node.js"></a>Node.js</h2><p>Hexo是基于Node.js构建的，所以我们需要下载TA</p><p>中文官网：<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn" title="点击下载">Node.js</a></p><p>建议下载长期维护版，相比于最新尝鲜版，长期维护版会更加稳定</p><h2 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h2><p>如果你要将你的项目推送到Github Pages或者Gitlab Pages,你会需要它，本文将以GitHub Pages作为示例，当然，如果你要使用自己的域名，也可能需要Git</p><p>Git官网：<a href="https://git-scm.com/" title="点击下载">Git</a></p><p>如果你的Git版本比Bayi的版本低或高，也许但未必会出现不兼容，报错的情况</p><h2 id="配置你的名称和邮箱"><a href="#配置你的名称和邮箱" class="headerlink" title="配置你的名称和邮箱"></a>配置你的名称和邮箱</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的git用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的git登录邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><ol><li>全局安装</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>初始化</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3. </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>上传GITHEB</li></ol><p>更改项目根目录的配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: （你的项目HTTPS地址）     </span><br><span class="line">  branch: main（你的默认分支）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-admin</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
